 room"},{"type":"entry","text":"smoking room 吸烟室","headword":"smoking room"},{"type":"section","text":"Step2 学以致用"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 1"},{"type":"example","text":"A：This office building is great. Don't you think so? （这栋办公大楼"},{"type":"text","text":"很棒。你觉得呢？）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：Yes, it definitely is. （是的，的确很棒。）"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 2"},{"type":"example","text":"A：Can you tell me how to use the fax machine? （你能告诉我怎么"},{"type":"text","text":"使用传真机吗？）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：Come on, I will show you. （来吧，我给你演示。）"}]},{"number":984,"blocks":[{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 3"},{"type":"example","text":"A：I think we need to buy a new copier. （我想我们需要买一台新"},{"type":"text","text":"的复印机。）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：I agree. （我同意。）"}]}]}